-- Warner Bros Reviewing Plans to Make The Hobbit Films in New Zealand
-- B y   T r a c y   W i t h e r s
-- 2010-10-21T20:04:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-21/warner-bros-reviewing-plans-to-make-the-hobbit-films-in-new-zealand.html
Warner Bros Productions Ltd. said
it is considering locations outside New Zealand for filming of
“The Hobbit.”  The actions of unions have caused substantial disruption
and damage and forced it to consider other options, the Los
Angeles-based company said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tracy Withers at 
 twithers@bloomberg.net  